{"tid":1825892,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點解羅致光可以係立法會亂鳩咁黎 用中止待續反擊得唔得","createTime":"2020-01-15T16:31:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-16T16:34:35.000Z","uid":210495,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"cede82c29ad878542af606081cda2e50125a5530","tid":1825892,"uid":210495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T16:31:53.000Z","msg":"話說就咁樣<br />\n<blockquote>（送中條例翻版）琴日立法會延長產假的條例草案繞過法案委員會交由人力委員會處理，係立國歌法，23條前奏！！！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1818445\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1818445</a></blockquote><br />\n議事規則54(4)明明係話<br />\n<blockquote>除與撥款法案有關者外，在負責法案的議員就現即二讀該法案的議案發言後，辯論須中止待續，而該法案須交付內務委員會處理，除非立法會就任何<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">議員</span></span></strong>在獲得立法會主席的同意後提出的一項可無經預告而動議的議案另有命令。</blockquote><br />\n羅致光係局長又唔係議員 點解佢可以提呢個議案<br />\n仲講埋咩<br />\n<blockquote>正如《議事規則》第 54（5）條，當政府將一條修訂 條例草案恢復二讀前，需要諮詢當時的內委會主席的意 見。所以，當然如果到適當時間可以提出（恢復二讀） 時，內委會已經恢復正常運作，即已經選出新任內委會 主席，屆時這個工作可以進行。不過，就算內委會未完 成有關選舉主席的工作也好，政府可以諮詢所有內委會 委員，當所有內委會委員均有受諮詢，這一定包括了前 任主席或將來的主席。大家知道，<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">將來與未來之間一線， 就是今天或此刻</span></span>，所以<span style=\"color: red;\">從延續性的角度而言，進行有關 《議事規則》第 54（5）條的安排諮詢全體內委會委員， 我們履行了這個責任諮詢內委會主席</span>。</blockquote>"},{"pid":"71c58a826fbf229ade8c93c57d6889646d2d7e06","tid":1825892,"uid":210495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T21:25:12.000Z","msg":"點解"},{"pid":"246787120cbbfe56da6317e7c1b345866e76561f","tid":1825892,"uid":167394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T21:30:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2857a29f2613365497965cb28f9f45a1c4307de","tid":1825892,"uid":808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T21:39:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bddf58e10ba2f67df57524d67831b361b90f53a","tid":1825892,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T22:47:59.000Z","msg":"羅：我話OK就OK"},{"pid":"63c2f371ffd7ffef2463b1ab0f2698be27dc26c2","tid":1825892,"uid":4780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T22:51:32.000Z","msg":"比你立法會贏撚晒建制都無撚用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb3d852f298536f38d03b0476988dca5526f9f95","tid":1825892,"uid":210495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"63c2f371ffd7ffef2463b1ab0f2698be27dc26c2","tid":1825892,"uid":4780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T22:51:32.000Z","msg":"比你立法會贏撚晒建制都無撚用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T05:44:15.000Z","msg":"點會"},{"pid":"2a611e249d68adebd7d100c33a6b734eaacd1377","tid":1825892,"uid":36441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"63c2f371ffd7ffef2463b1ab0f2698be27dc26c2","tid":1825892,"uid":4780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T22:51:32.000Z","msg":"比你立法會贏撚晒建制都無撚用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T05:46:58.000Z","msg":"主席係咩人做都重要既"},{"pid":"1d27ee0de1f48f1ad30ec6047d278d9ad5da668f","tid":1825892,"uid":194298,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fb3d852f298536f38d03b0476988dca5526f9f95","tid":1825892,"uid":210495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"63c2f371ffd7ffef2463b1ab0f2698be27dc26c2","tid":1825892,"uid":4780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T22:51:32.000Z","msg":"比你立法會贏撚晒建制都無撚用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T05:44:15.000Z","msg":"點會"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T05:47:03.000Z","msg":"有功能組別"},{"pid":"2d7bfcf6f3e7f04e70ff107218164b8ca0e08cd3","tid":1825892,"uid":210495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1d27ee0de1f48f1ad30ec6047d278d9ad5da668f","tid":1825892,"uid":194298,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fb3d852f298536f38d03b0476988dca5526f9f95","tid":1825892,"uid":210495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"63c2f371ffd7ffef2463b1ab0f2698be27dc26c2","tid":1825892,"uid":4780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T22:51:32.000Z","msg":"比你立法會贏撚晒建制都無撚用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T05:44:15.000Z","msg":"點會"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T05:47:03.000Z","msg":"有功能組別"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T16:34:35.000Z","msg":"過半可以否決政府議案"}]}